{"tid":1080892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"委內瑞拉再廣泛停電　馬杜羅多番指責美國發動網絡攻擊","createTime":"2019-03-28T02:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T00:23:07.000Z","uid":28765,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"996a6a847fe1beb3bd6a41ced06f696c0fd3bfd1","tid":1080892,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1450015_1_20190328010449.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1450015_1_20190328010449.jpg&h=6a2c3f64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n委內瑞拉首都加拉加斯再廣泛停電，全市漆黑一片。(美聯社)<br />\n委內瑞拉廣泛地區再度大停電，學校及商舖關閉。<br />\n<br />\n西方一個網上監察組織表示，委內瑞拉新一輪大停電導致全國91%地方，沒有電力供應。在首都加拉加斯，大部分商店關門，平日繁忙街道轉趨平靜，公共交通停駛。由於沒電力供應，電水泵停止運作，導致部分地區無水供應。<br />\n<br />\n總統馬杜羅多次指責大停電是由於美國網絡攻擊，破壞委內瑞拉輸電供應。自行宣誓為「臨時總統」的國會議長瓜伊多認為，是馬杜羅政府貪腐，公共設施日久失修引致大停電。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1450015-20190328.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1450015-20190328.htm&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTl0VeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=1444fdca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1450015-20190328.htm&h=ab7dc156\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1450015-20190328.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n真係美國佬整成咁都幾勁 打都唔使打"},{"pid":"cc3d5cc7f1908a85b90a6987036b4273f3da171a","tid":1080892,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:09:40.000Z","msg":"Die hard4"},{"pid":"db0ac22e37526733280e2228b4c9f4f06f4fafe8","tid":1080892,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:43:41.000Z","msg":"冇電冇水都未暴動， 呢個國家都幾特別"},{"pid":"a0253b5512d0edfd7676b03ced85bba1a241f5d4","tid":1080892,"uid":39855,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"db0ac22e37526733280e2228b4c9f4f06f4fafe8","tid":1080892,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"